The exotic Mövenpick Hotel Ibn Battuta Gate is a Moroccan themed, 5-star hotel with 396 rooms. This beautiful property is looking for Housekeeping Coordinator to join the team.
The candidate will provide administrative support to the Housekeeping team, assist in giving a consistent service to the departments that meets the hotel's standards, ensure guest requests specified by superiors are promptly and courteously met and promote the work culture and company's core values.
In addition to the above, candidate must atleast have 1 year experience in a similar role in a 5 star hotel. With an eye for detail and is able to provide high level of cleanliness. Also have a good knowledge of the English language, for excellent communication skills and is customer oriented for individual to have a thorough understanding and knowledge of rooms related service and product.
